name: be-octopath-traveler-cotc
description: Octopath Traveler is a video game that was originally released on the Nintendo Switch on July 13th 2018. It has been one of the most phenomenal JRPG games that I have been able to have ever played, and on July 27th 2022 - the prequel to the original Octopath Traveler game was released, this being "Octopath Traveler Champions Of The Continent".
